java.sql
Class Types

java.lang.Object
  |
  +--java.sql.Types
public class Types
extends Object

The class that defines the constants that are used to identify generic SQL types, called JDBC types. The actual type constant values are equivalent to those in XOPEN.

This class is never instantiated.
